---
import { company } from '../data/company';
---

<section id="contact" class="py-20 bg-white">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 text-center">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">お問い合わせ</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-600 mb-8">
      事業内容に関するご質問、コンサルティングのご相談など、お気軽にお問い合わせください。
    </p>
    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4">
      <a
        href={`mailto:${company.email}`}
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-8 py-4 bg-accent hover:bg-accent-dark text-white font-semibold rounded-lg transition-colors"
      >
        <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path d="M2.003 5.884L10 9.882l7.997-3.998A2 2 0 0016 4H4a2 2 0 00-1.997 1.884z"></path><path d="M18 8.118l-8 4-8-4V14a2 2 0 002 2h12a2 2 0 002-2V8.118z"></path></svg>
        メールで問い合わせ
      </a>
      <a
        href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/kenimo49"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-8 py-4 bg-[#0A66C2] hover:bg-[#004182] text-white font-semibold rounded-lg transition-colors"
      >
        <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M20.447 20.452h-3.554v-5.569c0-1.328-.027-3.037-1.852-3.037-1.853 0-2.136 1.445-2.136 2.939v5.667H9.351V9h3.414v1.561h.046c.477-.9 1.637-1.85 3.37-1.85 3.601 0 4.267 2.37 4.267 5.455v6.286zM5.337 7.433a2.062 2.062 0 01-2.063-2.065 2.064 2.064 0 112.063 2.065zm1.782 13.019H3.555V9h3.564v11.452zM22.225 0H1.771C.792 0 0 .774 0 1.729v20.542C0 23.227.792 24 1.771 24h20.451C23.2 24 24 23.227 24 22.271V1.729C24 .774 23.2 0 22.222 0h.003z"/></svg>
        LinkedIn DM
      </a>
      <a
        href="https://x.com/kenimo49"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-8 py-4 bg-black hover:bg-gray-800 text-white font-semibold rounded-lg transition-colors"
      >
        <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M18.244 2.25h3.308l-7.227 8.26 8.502 11.24H16.17l-5.214-6.817L4.99 21.75H1.68l7.73-8.835L1.254 2.25H8.08l4.713 6.231zm-1.161 17.52h1.833L7.084 4.126H5.117z"/></svg>
        X DM
      </a>
    </div>
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mt-4">企業様はメール、カジュアルなご相談はDMでもお気軽にどうぞ</p>
  </div>
</section>
